# Changelog

## v1.0.~

### Added or Changed
- Added this changelog
- Added readme documentation
- Grouped auth routes and page to '(admin)' group
- Started to implement i18n and l10n for (arabic and english)
- Started to implement theme (dark mode and light mode)

### Removed
- Some packages/libraries from acknowledgements I no longer use
- Removed detect-device package, and implmented device detection manually

## V1.1.~

### Added or Changed
- Changed landing page to include selecting account
- Modified landing page styles
- Added terms and conditions
- Added vendor agreement
- Added Geo Encoding and Place Autocomplete functionality
- Added weight, volume, unit, pieces per pack and benefits on products create page
- Added user consent for using cookie and location
- Added statistics chart display for dashboard
- Added functionality to upload assets prior to item creation

### Removed
- Removed Select Account page and It's routes
- Removed Discount from products create page
- Disable theme change toogle
- Made promotion image requried